Project Description

Burst Spinners: Tournament

Is a android/IOS game where the player do a series of tournaments with different spinners that can be win through the in-game currency or in app purchases. This are the different modes available in the game.

Tournament Mode: Choose your favorite spinner and participate in multiple tournaments around the world and become the number one in each one of them.

Survival Mode: Choose your favorite spinner, and participate in a battle until death, battle each spinner in the game and be the best of the best.

Team Battle: Battling alone is not easy, choose 3 spinners and participate in the multiple tournaments in the game, and make your team the best in the game.

Multiplayer Battle with your friends in private matches, or with players around the world with your favorite spinner
